jff.translation
Class JFFStringsImpl

java.lang.Object
  jff.translation.JFFStringsImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
JFFStrings
public class JFFStringsImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements JFFStrings

An implementation of JFFStrings.
When created, an instance of JFFStringsImpl will check in the INITFILE the language specified, then it will search in the LANGFOLDER a file with this name (with .txt as extension) and load the language written in it, using a JFFParser

Version:
%I%
Author:
Francesco Fornasini
